sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant AdminWeb
    participant API as AudioRecoveryController
    participant RecSvc as AudioRecoveryService
    participant FS as File Storage
    participant DB
    Admin->>AdminWeb: Mở trang "Orphan Audio"
    AdminWeb->>API: GET /api/audio-recovery/orphans
    API->>RecSvc: GetOrphansAsync()
    RecSvc->>DB: SELECT * FROM Audio a WHERE a.PoiId NOT IN (SELECT Id FROM POIs WHERE IsActive=1)
    DB-->>RecSvc: orphanAudios
    RecSvc->>FS: Check file exists cho mỗi audio
    FS-->>RecSvc: existFlags
    RecSvc-->>API: orphans + fileStatus
    API-->>AdminWeb: list
    Admin->>AdminWeb: Chọn audio + POI đích để restore
    AdminWeb->>API: POST /api/audio-recovery/{audioId}/restore {newPoiId}
    API->>RecSvc: RestoreAsync(audioId, newPoiId)
    RecSvc->>DB: UPDATE Audio SET PoiId=? , IsActive=1
    DB-->>RecSvc: ok
    RecSvc-->>API: ok
    API-->>AdminWeb: 200
    alt Xoá vĩnh viễn
        Admin->>AdminWeb: Bấm "Delete orphan"
        AdminWeb->>API: DELETE /api/audio-recovery/{audioId}
        API->>RecSvc: DeleteOrphanAsync(audioId)
        RecSvc->>FS: Delete file
        RecSvc->>DB: DELETE FROM Audio WHERE Id=?
    end
    AdminWeb-->>Admin: Refresh danh sách
